PrecisAmendment to the SCHEDULE to the INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS) ASSISTANCE ACT adding two international financial institutions: "Global Environment Facility Trust Fund" and the "Multilateral Fund for the Implementation of the Montreal Protocol on Substances that Deplete the Ozone Layer".

precis:
Amendment to the SCHEDULE to the INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (FINANCIAL
INSTITUTIONS) ASSISTANCE ACT adding two international financial
institutions:
"Global Environment Facility Trust Fund" and the "Multilateral Fund for
the Implementation of the Montreal Protocol on Substances that Deplete
the Ozone Layer".
